Wujie Gu (Gavin) | 顾悟杰
Architect of WLM (Wujie Language Model)
Defining structural design, dimensional logic, and protocol-layer specifications.

Scope: Architecture only. Not involved in engineering, code implementation, or model development. Technical integration is managed independently by partner institutions.

---
"无界语言模型不为被需要而生，它是通往其自身消亡的一座桥梁。
WLM is not designed to be a necessity, but a bridge to its own obsolescence."
